                            Forschungsumgebung / Beta maṣāḥǝft In Bybliotheca Vaticana,  Akademie der Wissenschaften in Hamburg</dc:publisher><dcterms:isPartOf rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu"/><dcterms:bibliographicCitation>LIT7725HomilyEpiph</dcterms:bibliographicCitation><dc:format>xml</dc:format><dc:language rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#language">en</dc:language><dc:language rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#language">gez</dc:language><dc:contributor>Alessandro Bausi</dc:contributor><dc:contributor>Massimo Villa</dc:contributor><rdf:type rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu/ChristianLiterature"/><rdf:type rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu/Homily"/><dc:title>Dǝrsān za-qǝddus Gabrǝʾel liqa malāʾǝkt za-yǝtnabbab ʾama 10wa9 la-miyāzyā za-darasa qǝddus ʾEṗifānyos ʾeṗis qoṗos za-hagara Qoṗros</dc:title><dc:title xml:lang="gez">ድርሳን፡ ዘቅዱስ፡ ገብርኤል፡ ሊቀ፡ መላእክት፡ ዘይትነበብ፡ አመ፡ ፲ወ፱፡ ለሚያዝያ፡ ዘደረሰ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ኤጲፋንዮስ፡ ኤጲስ፡ ቆጶስ፡ ዘሀገረ፡ ቆጵሮስ፡</dc:title><crm:P102_has_title rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT7725HomilyEpiph/title/t1" xml:lang="gez"/><dc:title xml:lang="gez">Dǝrsān za-qǝddus Gabrǝʾel liqa malāʾǝkt za-yǝtnabbab ʾama 10wa9 la-miyāzyā za-darasa qǝddus ʾEṗifānyos ʾeṗis qoṗos za-hagara Qoṗros</dc:title><dc:title xml:lang="en">Homily in Honour of St Gabriel the Archangel, for 19th Miyāzyā, composed by St Epiphanius, bishop of Cyprus</dc:title><dc:title xml:lang="en">Homily by Epiphanius, bishop of Cyprus, on King ʾAbrāsit and his son ʾAwǝr</dc:title><crm:P102_has_title rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT7725HomilyEpiph/title/t2" xml:lang="en"/><dcterms:hasPart rdf:resource="LIT7725HomilyEpiph/part/divLIT7725HomilyEpiph8"/><dcterms:hasPart rdf:resource="LIT7725HomilyEpiph/part/divLIT7725HomilyEpiph8"/></rdf:Description><rdf:Description rdf:about="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT7725HomilyEpiph"><saws:isAttributedToAuthor rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS7974PseudoE"/></rdf:Description><rdf:Description rdf:about="https://betamas